data.description: Assumable mortgage option at 3.55%. $3163 per month payments, and 340k remaining balance. Spacious 3 Bed, 2 Bath home with no HOA, perfect for year-round living, vacationing, or Airbnb hosting. Just 2 miles from the coastline, ideal for outdoor enthusiasts. The open-concept layout accommodates family gatherings and entertaining guests. The master bedroom is a tranquil sanctuary with an en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. The second bedroom offers comfort and privacy, while the third bedroom, with backyard access, serves as an ideal office space. Features include a 2020 AC, 2014 windows, laundry area, hurricane shutters, converted carport, and ample parking. Step outside to a  spacious backyard, with enough space for a pool, Tiki hut or a gazebo. Priced competitively to sell. Thanks.
